	* nasl/nasl_init.c (init_nasl_library) [HAVE_LIBSSH]: Define nasl
	constant "_HAVE_LIBSSH" by default.  Allow to disable it using
	OPENVAS_DISABLE_LIBSSH.  Remove use of envvar OPENVAS_USE_LIBSSH.

