	by Andre Heinecke.

	* doc/Doxyfile.in, doc/Doxyfile_full.in: Use @CMAKE_CURRENT_BINARY_DIR@.

	* CMakeLists.txt: Set minimum cmake version to 2.6.
	Use ${CMAKE_CURRENT_BINARY_DIR} and ${CMAKE_SOURCE_DIR}.

