	instead of OPENVAS_STATE_DIR.

	* misc/CMakeLists.txt: Define OPENVAS_DATA_DIR if it is set
	OPENVAS_DATA_DIR.

	* misc/services.h: Update define so OPENVAS_SERVICES points to the
	correct location.

