	* base/CMakeLists.txt, hg/CMakeLists.txt, misc/CMakeLists.txt,
	nasl/CMakeLists.txt, omp/CMakeLists.txt: Make CMake generated
	Makefiles less verbose to make it easier to spot compiler warnings.

